<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Come, behold the deeds of Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">the destruction he has caused on earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />He makes wars cease to the ends of the earth;</para>

<para style="q1">he breaks the bow and cuts the spear into pieces;</para>

<para style="q1">he burns up the shields.</para>
